sub_title: Managing Partner at yesshore IT recruitment / Talent Acquisition / Director of Stichting Share for Kids
summary:
I am the managing partner/director of Yesshore It Recruitment which is a Netherlands -Turkish software human resources company that helps clients solve their staffing needs.
YESShore provides well-trained IT talents and teams from Turkey.
I am also an attorney in Turkish law. My professional fields are commercial law and legal consulting. In the Netherlands, I graduated from a study programme at Leiden University Law Faculty comprised of Cyber Law and International Tax Law for Multinational Enterprises. Simultaneously, I work as a volunteer director in the foundation Share for Kids which is founded by me and works for the benefit of children.            
I am eager to work and learn. Team player and devoutness are the words that suit me.
